      "mitigation": "Build a batch backfill job that reads from the normalized model in paginated chunks and populates all four projections. Run during off-peak hours. This is a one-time cost. Design backfill to be resumable (track last processed order_id). Estimate: ~30-60 minutes depending on DB and batch size."
