      "src/read/projections/transit_time_projection.py — Updates transit_time_zone_projection from events",
      "src/read/projections/courier_performance_projection.py — Updates courier_performance_projection from events",
      "src/read/updater/projection_updater.py — Polls outbox, dispatches to projection handlers, marks events processed",
      "src/read/queries/dashboard_queries.py — Simple SELECT queries against projection tables",
      "scripts/backfill_projections.py — One-time batch job to populate projections from normalized data",
      "scripts/reconcile_projections.py — Nightly consistency check between write model and projections"
